orsade de pointes such as dizziness, lightheadedness, fainting, palpitation, irregular heart rhythm, shortness of breath, or syncope.', 'Synergism', 'Caution is advised when clozapine is initiated in patients receiving other psychotropic drugs.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/72388/', '', 'Amisulpride, Lumateperone, Pimavanserin', 'Clozapine', 1767369485);
